5 § 1388. STOCK SUPPLY AND EMERGENCY ADMINISTRATION OF
6 EPINEPHRINE AUTO-INJECTORS
7 (a) As used in this section:
8 (1) “Designated personnel” means a school employee, agent, or
9 volunteer, or practical nurse licensed pursuant to 26 V.S.A. chapter 28 who has
10 been authorized by the school administrator nurse to provide and administer
11 epinephrine auto-injectors and intranasal epinephrine under this section and
